# Onboarding screen conventions

Follow these patterns for **all onboarding slides** — current six and the next six.

## Architecture

- **One layout component**: `OnboardingSlide.js` — never create a per-screen component.
- **Data-only slides**: add entries to `ONBOARDING_SLIDES` in `onboardingSlides.js`.
- **Pager**: `OnboardingScreen.js` — horizontal `FlatList` + fixed footer (dots + Next).
- **Tokens**: `onboardingUi.js` maps to theme (`G`, `COLORS`, `SPACING`, `RADIUS`) — **never inline hex**.

## Layout rules

- **No `ScrollView`** anywhere — flex-only; content must fit without scrolling.
- **Only the image area uses `flex: 1`**; heading, subtext, lists, footer are fixed height.
- **Horizontal padding**: `ONBOARDING_UI.padX` on all content **including top image** (`topImageSection`).
- **Screen background**: `ONBOARDING_UI.cream` everywhere — **no card/surface boxes** behind lists or feature groups.

## Images

- Always use `OnboardingImagePlaceholder` (rounded, dashed placeholder, `IMAGE` label, `resizeMode="cover"` when sourced).
- Set `imageSource: null` until PNG wired in `assets/images/index.js`.
- `imagePosition`: `top` | `middle` | `bottom` | `none`.
- Bounds from `ONBOARDING_IMAGE` in `onboardingUi.js` (`minHeight` / `maxHeight` / `borderRadius`).

## Text & lists

- **Heading**: serif (`FONTS.display`), `ONBOARDING_UI.green`, ~24px centered or ~26px left.
- **Body**: sans, `ONBOARDING_UI.text`, 14px; centered slides may use `bodyMaxWidthRatio: 0.85`.
- **Welcome only**: `intro`, `showLogo: true` (`TrellisWordmark`), `footer: FOOTER.welcome`, `titleSize: 20`.
- **List variants** (`listVariant`):
  - `iconList` — icon + label rows via `bullets` or `featureBox: { title, items }` (plain, no card bg).
  - `checklist` — ✓ + label via `checklist: string[]`.
- Optional `lead` before list (left or center per `contentAlign`).

## Footer

- **Standard** (`FOOTER.standard`): pagination dots + full-width Next button (~52px, `ONBOARDING_UI.primary`).
- **Welcome** (`FOOTER.welcome`): compact Next only, no dots, aligned right.

## Adding slides 7–12

Append to `ONBOARDING_SLIDES`. Batch 2 (slides 7–12) uses **5 pagination dots** (screens 11–12 both show dot 5 active). Screen 12 uses `nextLabel: 'Continue'`.

Preview UI blocks (screens 8–12): set `blockVariant` + `previewBlock` data — rendered by `OnboardingPreviewBlocks.js` using theme card styles (`cardBg`, `cardBorder`). Screen 7 uses plain `listHeading` + icon rows (no card).

## Adding more slides

| File | Role |
|------|------|
| `onboardingSlides.js` | Slide copy + config |
| `OnboardingSlide.js` | Shared flex layout |
| `OnboardingScreen.js` | Pager + navigation |
| `onboardingUi.js` | Theme-mapped tokens |
| `OnboardingImagePlaceholder.js` | Illustration slot |
| `OnboardingPagination.js` | Dot indicator |
| `OnboardingFeatureIcons.js` | List icons |
